videos.description: Horace Spencer with a fancy behind the back pass to Malik Dunbar who drains a 3-pointer from the corner.
videos.headline: Tigers' start game off on 8-0 run

videos.description: Horace Spencer gets the ball off the rebound and kicks it out to Malik Dunbar who sink the triple from the top of the wing.
videos.headline: Auburns' Dunbar hits another 3-pointer

videos.description: Collin Sexton drains fade-away jumper seconds before the half-time buzzer. Crimson Tide trail 40-35 at the half.
videos.headline: Alabama's Sexton hits jumper before half-time buzzer

videos.description: Jared Harper knocks down a deep 3-pointer from the top of the arc.
videos.headline: Auburns' Harper drains triple from downtown

videos.description: Dazon Ingram cuts in towards the basket and slams home a two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Crimson Tides' Ingram slams home two-handed dunk

videos.description: Bryce Brown shows off his handle and hits the fade-away jumper.
videos.headline: Tigers' Brown shakes and bakes for a smooth jumper

videos.description: Auburns' Dazon Ingram turns the ball over and Charles Barkley mouths "slow down" after the turnover.
videos.headline: Sir Charles coaching from the stands

videos.description: Malik Dunbar hammers home the first dunk, and Horace Spencer jams in the put-back dunk, and Charles Barkley looks elated in the crowd.
videos.headline: Back-to-back Tigers dunks make Sir Charles happy
